data.description:
One owner and very well taken care of home in the heart of Olive Branch w/ many updates and upgrades!  Very nice 3br, 2 full bath home set on large fenced in cove lot!  This home offers all laminate wood flooring in all the rooms, updated light fixtures and plumbing fixtures, 4 yr old AC unit, newer appliances, and brand new vinyl energy efficient windows w/ warranty!  House has a large primary bedroom and impressive primary bathroom with dbl sinks, oversized corner jetted tub, and separate shower.  Kitchen area has breakfast area and dining room area or office.  On to the backyard paradise!  In the backyard, you have a new covered back patio w new decking, large fenced in yard, and above ground swimming pool (seller will remove pool if new owner doesn't want it).  There is also a hot tub on back deck that is negotiable. Storm glass doors on front and back too. 
 Very well-maintained home!
